data.Name: ROLE MODEL
data.Bio: Tucker Pillsbury, better known by his stage name ROLE MODEL, was born on May 15, 1997 in Portland, Maine and grew up in Cape Elizabeth, Maine. His father, Rusty, is a real estate appraiser, and his mother, Susan Pillsbury, is a special education teacher in Cape Elizabeth. He now resides in Los Angeles, California. American pop singer and songwriter who began to make waves in the music industry with the release of his 2017 EP Arizona In The Summer. Read more on Last.fm
